<ext_description linkend="Kinematic_topology_arm.Oriented_joint">
	An <b>Oriented_joint</b> is a type of
	<express_ref linkend="elemental_topology:arm:Elemental_topology_arm.Oriented_edge" />
	that is a direction of traversal of a joint.
	<note>
